{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_23212.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200601,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200900,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/calender_day16.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime11","chara":[{"id":200601,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-1"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I see...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-2"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So you've got a trick where you can turn@memories into film and cut 'em up, huh?"},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-3"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]You sure it's a good idea to show me@the ace up your sleeve like this?"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"textAvClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"effect":"ef_adv_05","face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"se":"7205_magic_girl"},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-4"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I want to equal things up,@if only a little."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp3.json","id":200601,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-5"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Equal?@What's this all about?"},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-6"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Doesn't it creep you out at all?"},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-7"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]You and I could have talked before@at some point."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-8"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]And I could know your every move..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200601,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-9"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So what?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-10"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Huh...?"},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-11"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Doesn't matter what kind of magic@you've got. I just do my own thing."},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-12"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]If you annoy me, I'll punch you. If you've@got an interesting deal, I'll join ya."},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"autoTurnNoDelay":1,"chara":[{"id":200601,"motion":300,"voiceFull":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-13"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]If you're suffering...well, I might@help you. If I feel like it."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200601}]},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-14","voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-13"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But... The more this loop repeats,@the farther apart we all become."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-15"},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200601,"motion":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]We become less and less equal..."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-16"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Even if it all starts off with an earnest@wish for someone else's sake..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-17"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]It starts to fade, bit by bit..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200902,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-18"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Our dynamics just keep changing..."},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-19"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]These loops or whatever?@None of that matters."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200902,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-20"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But..."},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-21"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]See, the REAL problem is wishin'@for other people's sake."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200601,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-22"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]You shouldn't ever wish for@another person..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200601,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-23"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]...At least, that's what I always thought."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200601,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-24"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Until I met Homura Akemi, that is."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-25"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Miss Akemi...?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200601,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-26"},{"id":200902,"motion":0}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]If I were in her shoes,@I would've already given up."},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-27"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I'd probably just be doin' whatever@the heck I want in the loops."},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-28"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]She's probably got somethin'@really important to her, right?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200601,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-29"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]No matter how many times she fails, she'll@never stop until she reaches that goal."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200601,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-30"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Somethin' so important, not even fate@can get in the way of it."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-31"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Not even fate...can get in the way of it..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-32"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Heh heh heh..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-33"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Yeah, that's true."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200902,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-34"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Miss Akemi's wish...isn't something@that she'll turn from easily."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-35"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Even if I get close to her,@she's not going to change..."},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"autoTurnNoDelay":1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":0,"voiceFull":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-36"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So the problem is with ME!@I need to figure out what I want to do!"},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"motion":400}]},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-37","voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-36"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Thank you, Miss Sakura."},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"autoTurnNoDelay":1,"chara":[{"id":200601,"voiceFull":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-38"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Mm?@Nah, it's nothin' to thank me over."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200601,"motion":100}]},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-39","voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-38"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I was the one that asked you@a weird question, so..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200601,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-40"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Oh, also."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-41"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Yes?"},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-42"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]What happens when Sayaka Miki makes@a contract for someone else's sake?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104212/vo_full_913116-015-43"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So, about that..."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
